Introduction

Hello, my name is Ethan Wang-So, and I am a student, programmer, and amateur web designer. I study computer science at the New Jersey Institute of Technology. You can read more about my education below.

I am currently based in New York. I am looking for any internship or co-op opportunities. I live in the New York-New Jersey area, but I am always willing to travel.

Education

I currently attend the New Jersey Institute of Technology located in Newark, New Jersey. I am a second year computer science major. I am involved with the Association for Computing Machinery and Filipinos In Newark Engaging In Socio-Cultural Traditions. I have done research on campus in the virtual reality facility under Dr. Margarita Vinnikov. I am also a Teacher's Assistant in the computer science department.



I graduated high school at St. Peter's Preparatory School in Jersey City, New Jersey.

Skills & Experience

I am knowledgeable in several programming languages such as Python, Java, C#, C++, PHP, and Javascript. I am also well versed in frameworks and libraries such as Django and React.
